title: CBB rigged? Stunned viewers suspect foul play as Coleen storms to victory
text:
CHANNEL 5 CONSPIRACY?: Viewers cooked up their own sensational theories blatantly a fix, i haven't seen anyone on here wanting coleen to win or have voted for her. what a joke #cbb — beth (@bethanmgc) 3 February 2017 
Still, there were some celebs who seemed happy with how things turned out. 
Aisleyne Horgan-Wallace wrote: “Massive congratulations to Coleen! Huge congratulations to @bbuk I’m so happy a decent woman won! This series was amazing! Well done.” 
Meanwhile Luisa Zissman gushed: “She was honest about her reasons 4 going in, i hope her marriage will be ok, & she has had a boost within herself.” 
And Saira Khan chimed in: "Bless her!!! @#cbbcoleen, you deserved it so much. Making me cry with so much happiness." What a coincidence that Coleen, Emma and Rylan have ITV as an association, and Coleen wins.Hmmm...
